This paper is about personalized recommendations, which is a common topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of regression trees also suggests a focus on decision trees and tree-based models, which are often studied in machine learning (cs.LG) and computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also mentions user-generated reviews, which could fall under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI) or cybernetics (cs.CY).
